  "readingTitle": "evaluate — Paper 4 — Writing & translation into Spanish",
  "reading": "Combine a routine, a preference and a plan: ‘Me levanto a las siete, prefiero el fútbol y voy a hacer mis deberes.’ At Higher, add gustar-type and a stem-changer to show range: ‘me interesan…’, ‘pido…’.",
